The Water trucking vendor reported that he sells water inside the city and is not going too far distance. The vendor reported that the water which is distributed doesn't need to be  chlorinated because the water is very pure and it is also used for drinking.

The water truking vendor reported that he dosn't go long distances outside the district because there are other vendors who have water trukings and people are taking from the nearest vendors in order to the water cost doesn't increase.

In the rural areas only some people who need water trucking because most of them depend on small projects provided by farmeres who have machines.
